items.title: Roblox Wikia
items.headline: ROBLOX Wikia: the free encyclopedia about ROBLOX that anyone can edit
items.desc: Roblox is a game playing, hosting and development platform used by millions of users who are the architects of their own worlds. The Roblox Wikia is a free encyclopedia about Roblox that anyone can read and edit. It contains information about aspects of Roblox, about scripting and the API used to develop games and about the community. It is edited by more than 300 different users every month and has more than fifteen thousand articles about Roblox.

items.name: Roblox Vehicle Simulator Wiki
items.title: Roblox Vehicle Simulator Wiki
items.desc: Roblox Vehicle Simulator is a simulator on Roblox.com which allows you to either drive, fly or sail a variation of planes, boats, and cars. Currently, there are 35 different branded cars in the game and more are coming in the future. Also, there is currently a Jetski, a Speedboat and a Stuntplane to choose from! At the start of the game, you start off with Chevy Impala, free of charge! Simply drive around to earn money and mileage to buy your next Vehicle. There are several races to choose from and they are scattered all across the map, these races consist of; Drag, Circuit, and Highway races! Have Fun!
